Firefox is a product of Mozilla.
This script try to download the lastes version of Firefox 4 from:
http://releases.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/firefox/releases/latest/linux-$ARCH/es-ES/
Where $ARCH is your machine architecture.
It's prepared for Spain.
Also a symbolic link in /usr/local/bin is created (named "firefox4")
It's recommended to create a new profile for Firefox4 (You can do it running "firefox4 -P", 
then you can run simply "firefox4".
